  "description": "Tell DVLA if you have Brugada syndrome. ",
  "details": {
    "body": "<p>You must tell DVLA if you have Brugada syndrome.</p>\n\n<div role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Warning\" class=\"application-notice help-notice\">\n<p>You can be fined up to £1,000 if you don’t tell DVLA about a medical condition that affects your driving. You may be prosecuted if you’re involved in an accident as a result.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2 id=\"car-or-motorcycle-licence\">Car or motorcycle licence</h2>\n\n<p>You mustn’t drive if you have suffered from either:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>a loss of consciousness or fainting</li>\n  <li>cardiac arrest</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><a class=\"gem-c-button govuk-button\" role=\"button\" data-module=\"govuk-button\" draggable=\"false\" href=\"https://www.driving-medical-condition.service.gov.uk/report\">Report your condition online</a></p>\n\n<p>You can also <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/h1-online-confidential-medical-information\">fill in form H1</a> and send it to DVLA. The address is on the form.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"bus-coach-or-lorry-licence\">Bus, coach or lorry licence</h2>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/voch1-online-confidential-medical-information\">Fill in form VOCH1</a> and send it to DVLA. The address is on the form.</p>\n\n",
    "external_related_links": [

    ]
  },
